As a Swiss collective, we like to collaborate with innovative companies from our country. When Patrick, the owner of @werenbach, approached us and explained he was making watches from space rockets we got really intrigued. Every watches he produces contains real rocket material that has been into space! A few members of the collective received a watch and are, therefore, owning a part of space history now. You too can own a part of space history: with the code MACH3340 you get 40% discount on www.werenbach.ch! #Werenbach #SpaceBorn #Mach33 #SwissWatch

Another interesting fact about hiking in Switzerland: there are almost as many kilometers of hiking paths as of roads in our country (65'000 km vs. 71'400 km). So if you want to try out all the hiking routes Switzerland has to offer, you'd better start now! On the day @luanbaruti hiked to this signpost near Leukerbad, he covered 0.003% of Switzerland's hiking paths üòâ.
